  // World Cup challenge
  '世界杯挑战模式：率领西班牙从四场友谊赛一路打进世界杯正赛。': 'World Cup Challenge: lead Spain through four friendlies and into the World Cup itself.',
  '安插眼线，严格规范球员私生活': 'Plant Informants and Strictly Police Players’ Private Lives',
  '作为一个严苛的主教练，你必须让球员们知道，在西班牙国家队的训练基地里，墙上的每项规定后面，都有一些双面胶。': 'As a strict manager, you must teach the players that every rule posted at Spain’s training base has a strip of double-sided tape—and an informant—behind it.',
  '与球员们一同参加聚会，喝无酒精饮料': 'Join the Players’ Party and Drink Alcohol-Free Beverages',
  '你当然说了不准喝可乐，但是有谁会听呢？你只能说服自己，至少你盯着他们，他们还不敢喝酒。': 'You banned cola, of course, but who listens? You reassure yourself that while you are watching, at least nobody dares touch the alcohol.',
  '每天乐呵呵地上班，毫不约束球员': 'Turn Up Cheerfully Every Day and Give the Players Total Freedom',
  '从苦难和高压下走出来的你崇尚快乐教育，于是你选择了给球员们最大限度的自由。很可惜，这个世界上的绝大多数人并不能理解这一点。': 'Having survived hardship and pressure, you believe in joyful coaching and give the players maximum freedom. Unfortunately, most people in this world do not understand your vision.',
  '亲自宣布首发竞争': 'Personally Announce Open Competition for Starting Places',
